WEBVTT

00:05:00.333 --> 00:05:01.875
Take Maine lobster.

00:05:03.250 --> 00:05:05.643
They don't look that romantic,

00:05:05.667 --> 00:05:07.226
or that kinky.

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:08.809
They are both.

00:05:08.833 --> 00:05:11.309
(Laughter)

00:05:11.333 --> 00:05:12.684
During mating season,

00:05:12.708 --> 00:05:16.476
female lobsters want to mate
with the biggest, baddest males,

00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:18.309
but these guys are really aggressive,

00:05:18.333 --> 00:05:21.792
and they'll attack any lobster
that approaches, male or female.

00:05:22.542 --> 00:05:26.184
Meanwhile, the best time
for her to mate with the male

00:05:26.208 --> 00:05:28.101
is right after she's molted,

00:05:28.125 --> 00:05:30.643
when she's lost her hard shell.